{"tid":588701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會補選還有不足四小時完結，截至傍晚六時半","createTime":"2018-03-11T11:44:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-11T11:44:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7dcef47d20adcac627d9496e35594e54a098a3a0","tid":588701,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-11T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=997065&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D997065%26csid%3D261_341&d=%2F4C5RZOQNvE4NBHarc2ArgRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=ebbb0c80\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=997065&amp;csid=261_341</a><br />\n<br />\n立法會補選還有不足四小時完結，截至傍晚六時半，有超過64萬9千人參與香港島、九龍西及新界東地方選區投票，投票率是30.91%。<br />\n<br />\n三區投票率分別是：<br />\n<br />\n香港島31.88%； 2016年換屆是41.58%<br />\n<br />\n九龍西32.67%；2016年換屆是40.37%<br />\n<br />\n新界東29.43%；2016年換屆是40.29%<br />\n<br />\n至於建築、測量、都市規劃及園境界功能組別補選，有超過3千9百人投票，投票率51.9%，較前年換屆選舉同一時段高0.59個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.881903.com/News_Images/NewsBoss/resize/20180311_20180311-184243.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FNews_Images%2FNewsBoss%2Fresize%2F20180311_20180311-184243.jpg&h=cd3b086d&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}